Mary Kay Stearns https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary_Kay_Stearns 0 Mary Katherine Jones (born October 27, 1925), better known by her stage name Mary Kay Stearns, is an American actress best known for portraying the fictional version of herself on the sitcom Mary Kay and Johnny from 1947 until 1950.
